{"id": "art-132", "label": "Art. 132", "title": "Art. 132", "slug": "art-132", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1091406725\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2281\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1091406725\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 132 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Hot&#259;rârile\nluate de adunarea general&#259; în limitele <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>\nsau actului constitutiv sunt obligatorii chiar pentru <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>\ncare nu au luat parte la adunare sau au votat contra.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Hot&#259;rârile adun&#259;rii\ngenerale contrare <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i> sau actului\nconstitutiv pot fi atacate în <span class=SpellE>justi&#355;ie</span>, în\ntermen de 15 zile de la data public&#259;rii în Monitorul Oficial al României,\nPartea a IV-a, de oricare dintre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> care\nnu au luat parte la adunarea general&#259; sau care au votat contra <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> au cerut s&#259; se insereze aceasta în\nprocesul-verbal al <span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;ei</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Când se invoc&#259; motive de\nnulitate absolut&#259;, dreptul la <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span> este\nimprescriptibil, iar cererea poate fi formulat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde orice persoan&#259; interesat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1251177648\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2280\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1251177648\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Membrii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv ai consiliului de supraveghere, nu pot ataca hot&#259;rârea\nadun&#259;rii generale privitoare la revocarea lor din <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ie</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_762456925\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2279\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_762456925\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Cererea se va <span class=SpellE>solu&#355;iona</span>\nîn contradictoriu cu societatea, reprezentat&#259; prin consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv prin directorat.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2107218687\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2278\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2107218687\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Dac&#259; hot&#259;rârea este atacat&#259; de <span\nclass=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> membrii consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nsocietatea va fi reprezentat&#259; în <span class=SpellE>justi&#355;ie</span>\nde c&#259;tre persoana desemnat&#259; de <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span>\n<span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> dintre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>\nei, care va îndeplini mandatul cu care a fost îns&#259;rcinat&#259;, pân&#259;\nce adunarea general&#259;, convocat&#259; în acest scop, va numi un\nreprezentant.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1780090729\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2277\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1780090729\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Dac&#259; hot&#259;rârea este atacat&#259; de <span\nclass=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> membrii directoratului, societatea va fi\nreprezentat&#259; în <span class=SpellE>justi&#355;ie</span> de c&#259;tre\nconsiliul de supraveghere.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(8)Dac&#259; au fost introduse mai\nmulte <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> în anulare, ele pot fi conexate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_19450504\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2276\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_19450504\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Cererea se va judeca în camera de consiliu.\nHot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259; <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;at&#259;</span>\neste supus&#259; numai apelului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1156328415\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2275\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1156328415\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Hot&#259;rârea definitiv&#259; de anulare va fi <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;ionat&#259;</span> în registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al\nRomâniei, Partea a IV-a. De la data public&#259;rii ea este opozabil&#259;\ntuturor <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) În interpretarea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> aplicarea <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 132 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> nr. 31/1990, republicat&#259;, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare, raportat la art. 116 din <span class=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span> <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>, pot fi atacate în <span\nclass=SpellE>justi&#355;ie</span>, cu <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span> în\nanulare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> hot&#259;rârile adoptate de adunarea\nspecial&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}